https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r6FTWe6PPj6rniNTEuoUMALdVUC.jpg They need protection: the church needs a miracle. Jack witnessed a mob murder, so the FBI relocates him and his wife, Julie, to a place the gangsters will never look: he's Associate Pastor at a half-dead church in Fresno. On Jack's first Sunday, the Senior Minister keels over dead in the pulpit. Can a fake minister be the answer to the church's prayers? Can I Get a Witness Protection?
